    <h1>Metacircular Evaluator</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Abelson &amp; Sussman &middot; 1996 &middot; <a href="https://mitp-content-server.mit.edu/books/content/sectbyfn/books_pres_0/6515/sicp.zip/full-text/book/book-Z-H-26.html#%_sec_4.1">SICP &sect;4.1</a></p>

    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none">A Scheme interpreter written in Scheme. <code>eval</code> dispatches on expression type, <code>apply</code> dispatches on procedure type. The mutual recursion between eval and apply is the whole story.</p>
    </div>

